<Content>Perfect getaway During our stay in Jakarta for several years, we have been to Bali many times, however this was our first time to stay in Villa Ixora. As family members from Europe were coming over to spend a few days with us in Bali, we were really looking for a nice relaxing place, where we could all stay together in one villa. Villa Ixora was the right place for us: the villa we stayed in (which has its own swimming pool) was very spacious and clean and it looked very beautiful with a mix of Balinese/modern architecture and decorations. We also really enjoyed the quiet and fresh atmosphere surrounding the place; it was great to be able to sit outside till late at night just chatting (and catching up with our family), something we hardly ever do in Jakarta! Also, the breakfast served in the mornings was perfect.We didn't make too many trips during our stay, but as for the few we made, Villa Ixora had made the arrangements for our transportation, which we found very convenient. Basically if you needed anything, you could always approach the owners or staff members; they were very helpful at all times. Overall our compliments for the hospitality of Helmut, Julia and the rest of the staff. They really made our stay very pleasant! If you're looking for a nice, quiet place, on a walking distance or just a short taxi drive away from shops and restaurants, where you can enjoy reading books, spending time with family and just get away from the stress of the big city, Villa Ixora is the perfect getaway! 
